import React from 'react'
import { Container, Form, Formwrap } from './signinelements'

const SignIn = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Container>
                <Formwrap>
                    <Icon to='/'>dolla</Icon>
                    <Formcontent>
                        <Form action='#'>
                            <Formh1>Sign in to your account</Formh1>
                            <Formlabel></Formlabel>

                        </Form>
                    </Formcontent>
                </Formwrap>
            </Container>
        </>
    )
}

export default SignIn
